{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Playful Finance Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* A soft, light background */\n            color: #333;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ff4f4f 100%); /* Brand Red Gradient */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #ff6b6b; /* Brand Red */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .services, .about, .contact {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin: 20px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border: 2px dashed #ff6b6b; /* Dashed border with brand red */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            background-color: #fff5f5; /* Slightly tinted background */\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(255,107,107,0.3); /* Softer red shadow */\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #ff4f4f; /* Darker Brand Red */\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .about p, .contact p, .contact form label, .contact form input, .contact form textarea {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        .contact form label {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .contact form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact form textarea {\n            width: 70%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 2px solid #ff6b6b; /* Brand Red border */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact form button {\n            background-color: #ff6b6b; /* Brand Red */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact form button:hover {\n            background-color: #ff4f4f; /* Darker Brand Red */\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #ff6b6b; /* Brand Red */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: auto;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Your Financial Funhouse!</h1>\n        <p>Making money matters less mopey and more marvellous!</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Playful Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Budgeting Bonanza</h3>\n                <p>Let's turn those numbers into a party!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Investment Island Adventure</h3>\n                <p>Set sail for financial freedom!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Debt Dragon Slayers</h3>\n                <p>Tame your debts with a smile!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Savings Superstars</h3>\n                <p>Watch your savings grow like magic!</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Our Whimsical Ways</h2>\n            <p>We believe finance doesn't have to be a drag! Our team of quirky consultants is here to guide you through the world of money with a lighthearted approach. We break down complex financial jargon into simple, fun, and actionable steps. Forget boring spreadsheets, let's make your financial journey an exciting adventure!</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Let's Connect!</h2>\n            <p>Ready to add some sparkle to your finances? Get in touch!</p>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Your Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Your Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Your Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send a Giggle!</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Financial Funhouse. All rights reserved. Let's get rich and have fun doing it!</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault(); // Prevent default form submission\n            alert('Thanks for reaching out! We\\'ll get back to you with a smile (and some financial wisdom)!');\n            // In a real application, you'd send this data to a server here.\n            this.reset(); // Clear the form\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}